import React from 'react'
import Head from 'next/head'
import AppLayout from "./components/AppLayouts"

const Profile = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <Head>
            <title>내 프로필 | NodeBird</title>
        </Head>
        <AppLayout>내 프로필 페이지</AppLayout>
        </>
    )
}

export default Profile
